Organization Name: FORT WORTH VETERANS HEALTH ADMINISTRATION VOCATIONAL REHABILITATION (VHA VR) | MAIN OFFICE | COMMUNITY BASED EMPLOYMENT SERVICES (CBES)/TRANSITIONAL WORK (TW)
Description: Provides rapid employment services to those who are work ready, along with vocational support and resources needed for a veteran to successfully transition to permanent competitive employment.

Organization Name: EASTERSEALS NORTH TEXAS (ESNT) | FORT WORTH CENTER | EMPLOYMENT SERVICES
Description: Provides employment services for persons with all types of disabilities and veterans. Services include supported employment, job readiness training, job coaching, job placement, job retention, and other services.

Organization Name: NATIONAL VETERANS OUTREACH PROGRAM (NVOP)- FORT WORTH | MAIN OFFICE | EMPLOYMENT AND TRAINING SERVICES
Description: Provides case management and employment counseling to veterans and non-veterans with wrap around employment and training services that help with stability and self sufficiency. Secondary services include job placement, suits for job interviews (veterans only), and other support services, such as bus passes.

Organization Name: FORT WORTH VETERANS HEALTH ADMINISTRATION VOCATIONAL REHABILITATION (VHA VR) | MAIN OFFICE | SUPPORTED EMPLOYMENT (SE)
Description: Provides employment services and long term support for honorably discharged veterans with severe mental illness (SMI).

Organization Name: GOODWILL NORTH CENTRAL TEXAS | STORE - HURST | VETWORTHY
Description: Provides job training and placement services for veterans and their families with the goal of achieving job placement, retention and long term financial stability.

Organization Name: GOODWILL NORTH CENTRAL TEXAS | CORPORATE OFFICE | VETWORTHY
Description: Provides job training and placement services for veterans and their families with the goal of achieving job placement, retention and long term financial stability.
